description: After a devastating earthquake hits Mexico City, trapped survivors from all walks of life wait to be rescued while trying desperately to stay alive.
acteurs: Demián Bichir, Héctor Bonilla, Oscar Serrano, Azalia Ortiz, Octavio Michel, Carmen Beato

description: When an army recruit is found dead, his fellow soldiers are forced to confront a terrifying secret that's haunting their jungle island training camp.
acteurs: Tedd Chan, Stella Chung, Henley Hii, Lawrence Koh, Tommy Kuan, Josh Lai, Mark Lee, Susan Leong, Benjamin Lim

description: With his vivid imagination, Simon the rabbit searches for fun while learning about the importance of responsibility and communication.
acteurs: Loti Bailey, Hayden Connett, Keith Faulkner, Rudy Greatorex, Luke Haliwell, Jacob Preston, Joanna Ruiz, Alex Starke

description: Honest, introspective comic Simon Amstell digs deep and delivers a uniquely vulnerable stand-up set on love, ego, intimacy and ayahuasca.
Young and heartbroken, a New Yorker travels to Paris to escape his romantic woes but is soon drawn into another all-consuming attraction.
acteurs: Brady Corbet, Mati Diop, Constance Rousseau, Lila Salet, Solo, Michaël Abiteboul, Nicolas Ronchi, Étienne Rotha Moeng

description: Eclectic stand-up comic Manu NNa relays everyday tales about the struggles of being gay in Mexico and shares his love of telenovelas and mezcal.
